<!-- Carousel Section -->
<div id="aboutUsCarousel" class="carousel slide mb-6" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <!-- Slide 1 -->
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
                    <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
                    <p>We are a team of passionate developers from CIT-University dedicated to building innovative solutions for businesses. Our project, Techett, is a ticketing system designed specifically for company setups. It helps businesses manage tasks, support requests, and internal processes efficiently. With Techett, we aim to simplify workflows, improve communication, and ensure seamless collaboration within organizations. Our goal is to create tools that empower companies to work smarter and achieve more.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 2 -->
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>What is Techett?</h1>
                    <p>Techett is a simple and reliable ticketing system designed to help companies manage tasks, requests, and support issues more efficiently. Whether it’s IT problems, HR requests, or team tasks, Techett keeps everything organized in one place. With easy tracking, clear communication, and quick resolutions, we help businesses save time and work smarter. Techett is here to make teamwork smoother and companies more productive.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 3 -->
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>The Purpose Behind Techett</h1>
                    <p>Manage tasks and requests in your company with ease. From IT issues to employee needs and maintenance tasks, our ticket management system helps you stay organized and efficient. Assign tasks, track progress, and resolve issues faster—all in one simple platform. Keep your team connected, improve communication, and ensure nothing gets missed</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
    </button>
</div>

